_sText:
I'll just say a few things, this is my first released map, I don't think it's bad for a first effort, but bear in mind that this is only v1, I'm planning more things for this map, including adding on the rest of the school, as this is based around my school, and I've had a lot of ideas from people and am hoping to bring them to reality. So all that's left to say now is...have fun and enjoy the map

P.S.You can use bots on there, and they like to camp and spring suprises on my map :)
